title: Jatin Saxena
summary: Jatin Sahay Saxena (born 4 August 1982) is an Indian first-class cricketer who plays for Chhattisgarh. He previously played for Madhya Pradesh. In January 2018, he was bought by the Rajasthan Royals in the 2018 IPL auction.
content:
Jatin Sahay Saxena (born 4 August 1982) is an Indian first-class cricketer who plays for Chhattisgarh. He previously played for Madhya Pradesh. In January 2018, he was bought by the Rajasthan Royals in the 2018 IPL auction.
